  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Stroke onset &gt; or = 6 months

          -  Able to walk without human assistance (may use walking aid)

          -  Sign informed consent form

          -  Approval from physician for participation in study

          -  Live in Belgium or in Benin

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  cardiac history of active unstable angina, recent (less than 3 months) myocardial
             infarction, or congestive heart failure

          -  orthopedic, circulatory, or chronic pain conditions restricting exercise;

          -  dementia;

          -  severe receptive or global aphasia with inability to follow 2-step commands;

          -  co-morbid non-stroke neurological disorder that impairs mobility (e.g. MS or
             Parkinson's);
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
